FBIS4-40166 "drsov115_a_94019" FBIS-SOV-94-115 Daily Report 14 Jun 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Military Instruction Course Taught With Georgia Military Instruction Course Taught With Georgia LD1406170794 Tbilisi CONTACT INFORMATION AGENCY in Russian 1327 GMT 14 Jun 94 LD1406170794 Tbilisi CONTACT INFORMATION AGENCY Russian BFN [Text] [No dateline as received] A joint course of instruction [uchebno-metodicheskiye sbory] involving division commanders from the Group of Russian Troops in the Transcaucasus and brigades of the Georgian Armed Forces begins in the Autonomous Republic of Ajaria on 16 June. The course program includes a regimental tactical exercise [polkovoye takticheskoye ucheniye] with a display of elements of the modern integrated all-arms battle and the sharing of experience in military training and army personnel education. The exercise will be attended by Russian army observers and senior military ranks from the Russian Federation Armed Forces.
